QuestData.Title: Yak Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Yak Soul is cordial and resilient. The shape of the yak will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Yak Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Yak Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, the yak. This shape is now yours to call upon.
